docs.snippet: VIRGINIA BEACH, Va., June 2 (UP)--Fay Crocker of Montevideo, Uruguay, won the fifth annual Triangle round-robin golf tournament today with a total score of 51 points.

docs.snippet: CHICAGO, June 3--Real estate appraisers from South America, as well as the United States and Canada, have taken the view that improved procedures in the determination of realty values may serve to stabilize investments in Latin American properties.
